{"tid":1062173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實究竟有幾多香港人係愛香港？","createTime":"2019-03-15T02:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T03:10:18.000Z","uid":241426,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"05d9a31897462143038dac7835ce265acd17b6fa","tid":1062173,"uid":241426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:17:11.000Z","msg":"我睇黎睇去呢，一係就英奴撚，成撚日係度miss old day但係根本係未撚出世。一唔係就啲笑人支那嘅港支，但係屋企老豆老母又係佢口中嘅阿支窩。<br />\n<br />\n務實啲啦，香港人。香港精神唔係「怨」呀屌你老母。"},{"pid":"db4bf189bf87e2679a2af4a54aeceadad8dbd696","tid":1062173,"uid":241426,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:25:52.000Z","msg":"我係屌祖籍支那又扮鳩本土嗰啲閪精，同埋嗰啲只要係洋腸有冇腐爛都塞落屎忽嗰啲契弟呀！吹咩？屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a36fe256762e75eee3bc68fe5103e6ff0d7d7b","tid":1062173,"uid":225768,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"db4bf189bf87e2679a2af4a54aeceadad8dbd696","tid":1062173,"uid":241426,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:25:52.000Z","msg":"我係屌祖籍支那又扮鳩本土嗰啲閪精，同埋嗰啲只要係洋腸有冇腐爛都塞落屎忽嗰啲契弟呀！吹咩？屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:28:38.000Z","msg":"你好叻呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e30d0aa620025179d39f4137b3bc8bb41bb6947","tid":1062173,"uid":241426,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:32:57.000Z","msg":"我就見到啲香港人係咁嘅：<br />\n<br />\n1）日本好正呀 香港好柒呀<br />\n2）英國嗰陣好好呀 宜家好柒呀<br />\n3）大陸支那好柒呀 但係錢要賺的<br />\n<br />\n奴得黎又幾有英姿窩"},{"pid":"40737a458d21990eaa69c932cab530cb5967cb01","tid":1062173,"uid":241426,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:40:09.000Z","msg":"所以喇，我就認為：<br />\n<br />\n97錢班有錢嘅香港人走撚曬，日日西人地方陽光沙灘，跟住係度話「我真係好愛香港。」<br />\n<br />\n冇得走嗰啲咪我呢啲窮撚，屋不嫐都冇嘅，工又唔識雞腸，又唔識煲冬瓜，但係都一樣冇怨過。<br />\n<br />\n回歸前後多新移民，個班新移民起碼都係大陸一流公民先可能黎到香港，帶埋啲北水落黎，都跟香港規矩做嘢。不過呢班人嘅後代呢，就自把自為以為自己係乜鳩「純血香港人」，四周圍屌人「支那」，收皮啦，你地都係雜種狗呀！"},{"pid":"0c9aa398b18735930e426b8e6276fd025661d2e8","tid":1062173,"uid":241426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:44:59.000Z","msg":"啲雜種狗日撚日話被入侵，鬼叫香港窮呀？<br />\n屌你老味你班友80年代90年代北上鱷魚頭老襯底，屌班支那妹時候就唔撚係入侵嘅！？<br />\n三十年河東 三十年河西 找你老豆屌人啲數喇！"},{"pid":"2728626c92c4ad9ff73009410708a15917dbf8f2","tid":1062173,"uid":137217,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 奇洛李維屍 )<br />\n返支那拜維尼啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd1d7990fc0cadf3c54e805df629e375c5c8397","tid":1062173,"uid":241426,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2728626c92c4ad9ff73009410708a15917dbf8f2","tid":1062173,"uid":137217,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 奇洛李維屍 )<br />\n返支那拜維尼啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:49:03.000Z","msg":"你唔撚洗拜嘅，收皮翻香港奶臭閪啦"},{"pid":"3a7c814b23f26858bb313be9bc6038fb5f93c7c5","tid":1062173,"uid":241426,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7bd1d7990fc0cadf3c54e805df629e375c5c8397","tid":1062173,"uid":241426,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2728626c92c4ad9ff73009410708a15917dbf8f2","tid":1062173,"uid":137217,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 奇洛李維屍 )<br />\n返支那拜維尼啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:49:03.000Z","msg":"你唔撚洗拜嘅，收皮翻香港奶臭閪啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:49:37.000Z","msg":"ps埋：你嘅香港係英屬殖民地呀"},{"pid":"a7c92babce2b149118a4bae935d95924949f9c9e","tid":1062173,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"有錢咪愛，國家無錢仲唔走？<br />\n香港人精神係錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}